com.taobao.datax.common.util
类 DbReaderProxy

java.lang.Object
  com.taobao.datax.common.util.DbReaderProxy

public class DbReaderProxy
extends java.lang.Object

A proxy which provides to database Reader plugin.
Usually this proxy is held by a Reader plugin. The proxy wraps ResultSet to line, then send line to Writer.

另请参见：
Reader, DbWriterProxy
